      "message": "Patch Set 1: Verified\n\nTests received by maloo, run on CentOS release 6.2/x86_64: (https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/124471da-d568-11e1-b078-52540035b04c).  Ran 12 tests.  No failures.",
