        "email": "adilger@thelustrecollective.com",
        "username": "adilger"
      },
      "date": "2012-07-24 15:07:56.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1: I would prefer that you didn't submit this\n\nPart of the reason this big exists is because there are two exit paths from the function. It would be better to consolidate the exit paths in some way, either by using a goto, or by moving all of the code under \"if (rc == 0)\".  \n\nProbably the second option is better, since there is little point in checking both \"if (rc != 0)\" and \"if (rc == 0)\" right after each other.",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
      "_revision_number": 1
    },
